1784405781822882	campaign_foundation	itc:v3:AWKSZk5M5ySTM5EAAAAAQatrrd1Vt0AAAAEzAw		item.comment	bn-qg0	{"body":"Implemented versioned YAML schema and fail-closed campaign plan compiler. Added deterministic DNS pinning, approved-CIDR checks, strict unknown-field/placeholder rejection, U64 checked arithmetic, mandatory ceilings/stop/evidence policy, authorization-reducing-only overrides, exact expanded steps/totals/filter/assumptions, fixtures and 18 tests. Integrated campaign and pinned PyYAML into the container. Verified unit suite, container smoke, positive/negative in-container CLI, and closed-loop SIP selftest."}	blake3:WEO_64O4Yq0Zm0tYOkhG4sZWIrh2-w5tp_sJYOP1sK0
