1784406153326625	campaign_runtime	itc:v3:AWKfOZmeTnzMQAAAAAAAQb7tt677YAAAAAEsAw		item.comment	bn-2cg	{"body":"Implemented supervised frozen-plan runtime and campaign run CLI. Each step runs in its own process group with per-step/global deadlines, bounded graceful-to-forceful cleanup, stable signal/timeout/failure exit codes, exclusive append-only v1 JSONL events, and a 32x4KiB bounded output queue with a 256KiB default persistence cap. Added event JSON schema, runner protocol docs, golden ordering fixture, and loopback-only fake runner tests covering success, crash, partial startup, timeout, descendant cleanup, output flood, idempotent cleanup, SIGINT, and SIGTERM. Verified 25 campaign/runtime tests (including runtime twice), 15 concurrent oracle tests, Python compileall, shell syntax, and shellcheck. No network traffic or temporary network state was created."}	blake3:Lk70-EhjWJUYbqJzL-EwEoRlPnYfEiU_62EzKfNxZ2g
