1784408265516988	packet_oracle_schema	itc:v3:AWKSTMnnJJJM5kxAAAAAQara91VW7WAAAAE0EA		item.comment	bn-39r	{"body":"Exit gate passed. Implemented `./bin/sippycup assert CAPTURE --expect FILE [--format human|json]`, versioned per-dialog/per-stream result output, stable exit codes 0 pass/1 assertion/2 expectations/3 capture/4 inconclusive/5 internal, canonical human+JSON projections, unknown-policy enforcement, examples, container integration, and operator docs. Golden/mutation corpus covers UDP/TCP, IPv4/IPv6, pcap/pcapng, early media, re-INVITE, fork, loss/reorder/duplicate, DTMF, one-way, third-party endpoint, post-BYE leak, physical truncation, and malformed disagreement. Evidence: 65 oracle tests pass; 50 campaign/runtime tests pass; deterministic JSON, human parity, failure frame/time linkage, privacy exclusions, and every exit code are tested. Performance gate: 20,000 RTP packets in 1.264252s with 3,942,782-byte peak analysis allocation (limits 8s/128MiB). Image 506670cc41de rebuilt; smoke and closed-loop SIP selftest pass; in-container oracle on signaling-only selftest returns expected failure for media.directionality. Parent bn-1da intentionally remains manual-close."}	blake3:2lgU8kgNmNqnWuGYW0sU4XQzaTp8M5jq0z5qTFa4ZsE
