1784410975085695	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErmQE		item.comment	bn-2et	{"body":"Implemented strict seeded chaos profile compiler and reviewed clean/fixed-delay/jitter/burst-loss/constrained-uplink/reorder/duplicate/MTU/asymmetric corpus. Compiler binds and revalidates topology snapshot/target digests, complete canonical flower selectors, attachment safety, capabilities, direction/duration, bounded values, queue contracts, and deterministic per-direction netem seeds; emits structured dry-run argv only. Added CLI, schemas, container assets, docs, and 12 focused tests. Evidence: make chaos-profile-test PASS (12); python3 -m unittest tests.test_chaos_profiles tests.test_chaos_topology -v PASS (22); python3 -m unittest discover -s tests -v PASS (113); jq empty schemas PASS; tc local help confirms emitted netem seed/gemodel/reorder/duplicate and TBF option forms."}	blake3:Aa5n-hXqh8ow3B-4eMrEbM03OhIJhL35nfMP_f4HxKM
