1784413627129391	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErxAE		item.comment	bn-1w3	{"body":"Implemented immutable sippycup envelope plan/run contracts with all eight required hard maxima (CPS, concurrency, media PPS, total calls, duration, hold, cooldown, recovery deadline), strict U64 checked arithmetic, one-dimensional low-start ramps, conservative per-step/global worst-case budgets, reviewed-manifest SHA rebound, and exclusive outputs. All CLI maxima only lower source authorization. The deterministic network-free controller gives stop > pause/resume > ramp precedence, rechecks call and wall-clock recovery budget before every step, and cannot resume past the global deadline. Added strict schema, Ferivox example, operator docs, launcher/container/smoke integration, and synthetic healthy/pause/stop/tamper/overflow/budget endpoint coverage. Evidence: focused envelope gate 18/18 pass; full shared suite 190/190 pass; JSON and shell syntax plus git diff check pass; manual lowered plan has 4 levels, 200 worst-case calls, and 230 total reserved seconds."}	blake3:pWMYez9w3GGaavmEXeyAjaYvztejBXsO7wQcPjJTsxI
