1784414010688672	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAEryAE		item.comment	bn-30k	{"body":"Implemented portable evidence packs and supply-chain/CI workflow. Deterministic USTAR output contains pack-manifest.json plus exactly the embedded evidence manifest inventory; fixed order/mode/uid/gid/mtime. Workspace-independent streaming verification rejects modified size/hash, missing, duplicate, traversal/control/dot paths, non-regular and undeclared members, duplicate/reserved declarations, invalid metadata, relabeled sensitivity, embedded content-identity drift, pack/evidence inventory mismatch, malformed image digest, and invalid minimal SPDX 2.3 record. Content and signature have independent statuses/verdicts; CLI exits 1 for content failure, 3 for minisign signature failure, 2 for configuration/tool error. Optional minisign and age are external adapters only: no key creation/import/storage/deletion; secret/public/identity paths remain caller-owned. Recipient encryption uses a mode-0700 temporary directory, atomically publishes only ciphertext, and removes plaintext on success/failure. CI export defaults to JSON/Markdown/JUnit/manifest only and copies an artifact solely by exact explicit --include-artifact, recording sensitivity and explicitlySelected. Added sippycup-pack CLI, evidence-pack-v1 schema, docs/README, age/minisign container packages, and smoke checks. Adversarial focused tests: 6/6 pack, 12/12 pack+privacy, 15/15 integration. Full repository: 199/199. Real container E2E passed plain create/verify, actual minisign key/sign/verify, actual age recipient encrypt/decrypt/reverify, and reports-only export; CI contained no source artifact. Exact final image 3f3972ca4d3b..., smoke confirms age, age-keygen, minisign, sippycup-pack. No commits."}	blake3:aMbQmYJTqlvcQkcFj_G41DxViBmrLHjqtdhyjFIWHDY
