1784414356738127	bob-dev	itc:v3:AWKc55JPnzzNAAAAAAAAQbu9V997YAAAAAErywE		item.comment	bn-1id	{"body":"Exit gate implemented and green. Repro runner: bin/chaos-exit-gate + tools/chaos_exit_gate.py; contract/limits: docs/CHAOS-EXIT-GATE.md. Final real rootless Podman evidence: work/chaos-exit-gate-final3-bn1id. All 9 reviewed profiles passed with requested effects observed, independent unshaped controls at 0% loss, lifecycle state=succeeded/restored for every run, and trafficStoppedBeforeTopologyTeardown=true. Every traffic CapEff was 00000000800425fb (NET_ADMIN bit 12 and SYS_ADMIN bit 21 clear). Controller pre/post snapshot SHA identical: 2734694dfef40affd121c2608af713351993e8b861bfa48ec496fd811907f7d9. Canonical host route pre/post SHA identical: 4281669a4c6400be603f5555659f96be774983270319dbc1d0522110b6397f6f. Host qdisc pre/post SHA identical: c30363d97f891793ae029697bb2a14f0be9066e7005133d79060c331607f8129. Host loopback heartbeat 520/520, 0% loss. Raw host route snapshots retained; canonical comparison removes only volatile expires/expires_ms/used countdowns, documented explicitly. Real negative probes in work/chaos-exit-negative-bn1id: missing /dev/net/tun reports pasta=unavailable and refuses topology; exact dangerous confirmation still refuses rootless execution before mutation. Adversarial tests cover all profiles namespace confinement, unavailable/unknown states for every required capability, dangerous confirmation grammar/rootful boundary, partial mutation rollback, signals/killed child, ownership changes, command/path tampering, and snapshot drift. Verification: focused chaos 41/41 PASS; full discovery 210/210 PASS in 75.748s; shell/Python/JSON syntax checks PASS. Rootless probes additionally found and fixed frozen snapshot ordering, private-/proc forwarding sysctl view, and explicit TUN detection/launcher pass-through. No commits."}	blake3:drev2VZqEZRzpwc2zS4PGjT3kRPd9j7xJWjJ47AgZA8
